# Applies only to examples/echo/Dockerfile (Docker's per-Dockerfile ignore-file convention),
# even though the build context root is csharp/. Keeps host-local build artifacts and version
# control metadata out of the build context — the Dockerfile COPYs its inputs explicitly, so
# none of this is actually needed, but excluding it keeps `docker build`'s context-upload step
# fast regardless of what's lying around in a given checkout.
**/bin/
**/obj/
gen/
.git/
